<https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/Cabling#CableDistributorDisconnector> a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "CableDistributorDisconnector" ;
    rdfs:comment """Cable distributor is a device where one set of cables terminates and (mostly) connect to another greater set of cables that lead to other terminators.
Typically <u>housed </u>in a track side cable disconnection box (lineside "mushroom" disconnection box).
Often contains a disconnector.
NR: Cable disconnector""" ;
    rdfs:subClassOf <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/Cabling#CableJointInstallation> .

