<https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/Local_operating_area#LozReleaseInstrumentRelation> a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "LozReleaseInstrumentRelation" ;
    rdfs:comment "A key release instrument for taking/handing back the local operating zone.",
        """needsKeyPresenceForReturn
True: The key must be locked inside the key release instrument before the local operating zone can be taken from/handed back to the signaller.

False: the interlocking doesn't check the presence of the key before taking/handing back the zone.""" ;
    rdfs:subClassOf [ a owl:Restriction ;
            owl:onProperty <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/Local_operating_area#appliesToReleaseInstrument> ;
