<https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/ETCS#EpsSignalProperties> a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "EpsSignalProperties" ;
    rdfs:comment "Encounter Prohibition System (EPS) is a signalling function that prevents trains encountering in a dual-track single-bore tunnel.",
        """EpsReportingPoint
True when the signal reports to the system that prohibits train encounters in the tunnel. 
The signal may be located outside and in advance of the tunnel. 
de-DE: Meldepunkt f&#252;r das Tunnelbegegnungsverbotssystem""",
        """EpsTunnelSignal
True when this signal implements the EPS.
False otherwise.""" ;
    rdfs:subClassOf <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Common#BaseObject> ;
    owl:disjointWith <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/ETCS#BaliseGroupLinking>,
        <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/ETCS#BaliseGroupProperty>,
