        <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/National_implementations/DB/ETCS#PredefinedEtcsTelegramSet> .

<https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/Assets/Controller/EULYNX_standard_interfaces#SxiConnection> a owl:Class ;
