<https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/Flank_protection#FlankProtection> a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "FlankProtection" ;
    rdfs:comment """Flank protection prevents rolling stock from unintentionally entering the train's route body.
Flank protection is given when selected elements, notably points, prove a given state.""",
        """remote
When flank protection measure is remote, the remote flank protection measure is given. 
de-DE: Fernschutz. Der Flankenschutz wird durch das n&#228;chste Flankenschutzelement hergestellt. (Ersatzschutzma&#223;nahme)""" ;
    rdfs:subClassOf <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Common#ConfiguredBaseObject> .

<https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Project_management#TimeFrame> a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "TimeFrame" ;
    rdfs:comment "Describes the time periods to which the railway equipment and layouts will be attached. The time periods may be specified as actual dates or as sequences. Time Frames may overlap. Several Time Frames may occupy the same spot in a sequence, allowing options to be specified.",
        """name
The name of the Time Frame, e.g. the project phase.""" ;
    rdfs:subClassOf [ a owl:Restriction ;
            owl:onProperty <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Project_management#note> ;
            owl:someValuesFrom xsd:string ],
        <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Common#BaseObject> .

