        <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/ETCS#EtcsTextDisplayStartCondition>,
        <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/ETCS#StandstillDetectionForShunting> .

<https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/Local_operating_area#LocalOperatingZone> a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "LocalOperatingZone" ;
    rdfs:comment """A local operating area consists of at least one local operating zone. The zone groups elements that can be worked locally. 
Zones can be disjoint, touch or even overlap. Adjacent zones can be independent, or can merge into a bigger zone to allow seamless shunting movement between them. Local control over the zones is taken in a given order, given by rank, e.g. 1-2-3. Handing back control is the inverse- operation, e.g. 3-2-1.""" ;
    rdfs:subClassOf <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Common#ConfiguredBaseObject> ;
    owl:disjointWith <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/Local_operating_area#LocalOperatingArea>,
        <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/Local_operating_area#LocalOperatingAreaUiElement>,
        <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Signalling/Local_operating_area#LocalOperatingZoneLimit> .

<https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Common#ReferenceDrawing> a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "ReferenceDrawing" ;
    rdfs:comment """Pointer to (a set of) reference drawings (aka control drawings) for civil and mechanical engineering purposes. May range from a reference to paper documents to 3D CAD-files.
National end-users can tailor this class to their needs.
Not to be used for drawings of <i>specific </i>objects: instantiate an Attachment class instead.""",
        """other
In case 'other' is chosen, a reference drawing must be referred to.
de-DE: sonstige; bei Auswahl des Werts 'sonstige' ist eine Profilzeichnung als Reference Drawing beizulegen.""" ;
    rdfs:subClassOf [ a owl:Restriction ;
            owl:onProperty <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Common#name_ReferenceDrawing> ;
            owl:someValuesFrom xsd:string ],
        [ a owl:Restriction ;
            owl:onProperty <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Common#subtitle> ;
            owl:someValuesFrom xsd:string ],
        [ a owl:Restriction ;
            owl:onProperty <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Common#parameterizedBy> ;
            owl:someValuesFrom <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Common#ReferenceDrawingParameter> ],
        [ a owl:Restriction ;
            owl:onProperty <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Common#variant> ;
            owl:someValuesFrom xsd:string ],
        [ a owl:Restriction ;
            owl:onProperty <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Common#title> ;
            owl:someValuesFrom xsd:string ],
        <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Common#ConfiguredBaseObject> ;
    owl:disjointWith <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Common#LocationProxy>,
        <https://cdm.ovh/edp/EULYNX_DataPrep/Generic/Common#View> .

